column2: SELECT p.ra,p.dec,p.petroMag_u,p.petroMag_g,p.petroMag_r,p.petroMag_i,p.petroMag_z,p.petroMagErr_u,p.petroMagErr_g,p.petroMagErr_r,p.petroMagErr_i,p.petroMagErr_z,p.extinction_g,p.extinction_i,p.extinction_r,p.extinction_u FROM BESTDR7..Galaxy AS p 	JOIN #x AS x ON x.objID=p.objID JOIN #upload AS u ON u.up_id = x.up_id   ORDER BY x.up_id
